10. Display/monitor intelligence:
   - Investigate what the IntelliJ Platform and JVM can actually expose about:
     - monitor DPI / scale
     - display bounds
     - graphics device id
     - IDE window location
   - Implement the best safe approximation available
   - If true DPI cannot be reliably determined cross-platform, fall back to matching by:
     - display bounds
